            <title>MDrop 0.2.3</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 07:41:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>MDrop 0.2.3</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Shows the selected files in Finder without leaving the floating Shelf in front.</li>
                    <li>Applies the fix to the detail tile, list double-click, and compact Shelf menu.</li>
                    <li>Runs the filename marquee only while hovered, eliminating its idle CPU usage.</li>
                    <li>Keeps the Shelf data available for reopening from the menu bar.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
